data.actual_result: There is a warning even if you didn't change anything
data.expected_result: There should be no notification unless you did change things
data.short_description: When you create an NSFW channel and don't accept the warning, go into the channel settings & it'll say you have unsaved change
data.steps_to_repro: - Create an NSFW channel - Don't accept the warning - Go into the nsfw channel settings - you should have a "Careful, you have unsaved changes!" warning even though you didn't do anything
